      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs tas Kehninsch/ nn apsehdehs Wahrtis. Un wiſſeem Laudim ktua stahstihts un tazzijts: Rungi/ tas Kehninsch fehd Wahrtis. Tad nahze wiſſi Laudis preeſſch ta Kehnixa. Bet Israels behdse ikkatrs kawa Dshwokli."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſi Laudis wiſſas Israeta Ziltis bahrahs/ un tazzija: Tas Kehninsch irr muhs no muhsu Eenadneeku Rohkas isglahbis/ un irr muhs atswab- binajs no to Wilistexu Rohkas/ un nu buhs winnam no Semmes tsbehgt preeſſch Absaloma."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir Absaloms/ ko mehs par Kehnizu bijam pahr mums fwatdijschi/ irr Katra nomiris/ nu tad/ kapehz effat juhs ktuffu/ to Kehnizu attkat pahrwest?"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhtija tas Kehninsch Dahwids pee teem Preestereem Zadaku un Abjataru/tazzidams: Runnajeet us teem Wezzajeem no Juhda/ un fakkajt: Kupehz gribbat juhs tee pehdejee buht/ to Kehnizu atpakat west us fawn Namnu? (jo wiſſa Israeta Walloda bja jaw pee ta Kehni- xa nahkuſi winna Namnu.)"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Juhs effat manni Brah- ki/manni Kauli un mannas Mee- jas effat juhs/ kapehz tad grih- bat juhs tee pehdejee buht to Keh- nizu attkat atwest?"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un us Amasu fakkajt: Neggi tu effi manni Kauli un manna Meeja? Lai Deews man fcha un taidarra/ ja tu par Katra"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Peel-Rungu ne buhſi maña Preek- scha/ wiſſa Latka Joaba Weeta.\nTä lohzija wiſch wiſtu Wihru no Juhda Sirrt/ ka weena weeniga Wihra/ un tee fuhtija pee ta Kehnina/(fazzida- mi:) Greesees atpakat/ tu un wiſſi tawi Kalpi."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tä greesehs tas Keh- ninsch atpakat/ un nahze pee Jardana/ un Juhda nahze us Gilgalu taun Kehnixaim prettie- eedans/ ka tee to Kehnizu pahr to Jardanu westu."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Simejus GerusDehts/ ta Dehla Zemini/kas no Baku- rim bija/ steidsehs/ nn nonahze ar teem Wihreem no Juhda/ taun Kehnizam Dahwidam pretti."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tuhkſtoschi Wihri no Benjamiza ar winnu. Ir Zih- bus Saula Naimma Sullainis/ ar faweem peezpadeſmits Deh- leem/ un faweem diwidesmits Kalpeem/ un tee zehlehs tikkuſchi pahr to Jardann ta Kehnixa Preeſſcha."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas Vlohsts pahr- zehlahs/ ta Kehnixa Namnu pahrwest/ nn padarriht/kas win- nam patifke. Tad nomettehs Simejus Gerus Dehts/ preeſſch ta Kehnixa femmē/ kad wiſsch pahr to Jardanu zehlehs/"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſsch tazzija us to Kehnizu: Ne peelihsfuit man mans Kungs to Nosegamnn/ un ne peeminni to/ ka taws Kalps tew irr gruhtu darrijs tai Dec- na/ kad mans Kungs tas Keh-"
    }
  ],
